overview: Evilyn slips away from class to grab a quick smoke in the bathroom. Mr. Chambers follows her to the girl's room, but when he finds her she's busy working herself to climax. Carmen gets called down to the principal's office to see Mr. Roberts. Carmen has no respect for any of her elders or fellow students. Mr. Roberts feels that a good spanking is in order. Maybe that will teach her a lesson. Natalie bets her friend $50 that she can get the janitor to stick it to her. Pete refuses at first, but Natalie has a way of getting what she wants. While writing an exam Manuel and Lilly make plans to hangout later. Lilly threatens Manuel to do what she wants or it's over, so Manuel gives her a deep dicking that she will never forget.
title: Corrupt Schoolgirls 5
